Description: scim-wijesekera is a SCIM module for the Sinhala Wijesekera keyboard.
 .
 SCIM (Smart Common Input Method) is an input method (IM) platform.
 .
 This module implements the keyboard layout described in 
 the "Sri Lanka Standard 1134:2004" document.
